{"tid":1041901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打好鍾意扮男人？","createTime":"2019-03-01T07:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T16:39:32.000Z","uid":130471,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e29eeb4ba2070198999a71a3c7117857f623053","tid":1041901,"uid":130471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:43:58.000Z","msg":"有個朋友好鍾意Flirt佢身邊啲女性朋友<br />\n但佢係直到冇得再直既女仔黎 <br />\n<br />\n佢仲好鍾意係網上講啲變態野 嚇到啲囡囡block9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正臭閪影衰晒啲男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問佢點解要咁做 <br />\n佢話咁樣做到平時唔夠膽做既野 又覺得Flirt仔仔太唔矜持<br />\n<br />\n唔止咁 佢仲會扮hehe去撩啲直男<br />\n搞到啲直男屌鳩佢老母<br />\n<br />\n明明外表都正正常常一個女仔 但一開口就勁麻甩<br />\n啲連登tone出晒黎 開口埋口都話自己冇女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打可以解答我咁做有咩意義呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢係唔係上連登上壞腦呀？"},{"pid":"15bba3671bc22b04570c7e58ecc7f7bf609bddf0","tid":1041901,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"樓主白卡佬"},{"pid":"03bbf704b231fdbc1b0afce647f46b7439abf625","tid":1041901,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬白卡佬"},{"pid":"67e72bb29f4c2c82282755b60f29d16c32197809","tid":1041901,"uid":130471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15bba3671bc22b04570c7e58ecc7f7bf609bddf0","tid":1041901,"uid":148185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"樓主白卡佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"可唔可以討論番正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a3e0c8fabc9f3d730ebb9732e6c96997d650e4","tid":1041901,"uid":130471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03bbf704b231fdbc1b0afce647f46b7439abf625","tid":1041901,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"樓豬白卡佬"},"citedBy":0,"repl